local BlockPlayer = require "actions/BlockPlayer" local Parallel = require "actions/Parallel" local MessageBox = require "actions/MessageBox" local Ease = require "actions/Ease" local Do = require "actions/Do" local Wait = require "actions/Wait"
return function(self, player) if GameState:isFlagSet("tutorial:hide_pillar6") then return end
if not self.hideTime then self.hideTime = 0 end if player.showPressDir == "pressleft" and love.keyboard.isDown("left") then self.hideTime = self.hideTime + love.timer.getDelta() else self.hideTime = 0 end
local pillar = self.scene.objectLookup.Pillar2 if self.hideTime > 3 then GameState:setFlag("tutorial:hide_pillar6") self.scene:run( BlockPlayer { MessageBox {message="Computer: Excellent work.", sfx="choose"}, Do(function() self.scene.objectLookup.Cursor.x = pillar.x + pillar.sprite.w self.scene.objectLookup.Cursor.y = pillar.y + pillar.sprite.h*2 - 32 - player.height*2 end), Parallel { Ease(self.scene.camPos, "x", player.x - pillar.x, 1), Ease(self.scene.camPos, "y", player.y - pillar.y - pillar.sprite.h*2, 1), MessageBox {message="Computer: Now hide behind the pillar just above you, and look down."} }, Parallel { Ease(self.scene.camPos, "x", 0, 1), Ease(self.scene.camPos, "y", 0, 1) } } ) end end
